The paper discusses machine learning-based approaches for question answering systems, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing (NLP) modules, which is a subfield of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of external NLP modules may also involve deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of knowledge bases, which is a subfield of databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper proposes a new approach for question answering systems, which may involve software engineering techniques (cs.SE).
